    "For most of the layers, bias was eliminated as per Chowdhery et al. (2023).",
    "However, bias was added in the QKV layer to enhance the model's extrapolation capability.",
    "The traditional layer normalization technique described in Ba et al. (2016) was replaced with RMSNorm.",
    "They chose SwiGLU as their activation function, which is a combination of Swish Ramachandran et al. (2017) and gated linear units (Dauphin et al., 2017).",
    "The dimension of the feed-forward network (FFN) is also reduced."
  ],
